For accepting to watch this video,  allowing us to share with you God's Blessings,  reminding us to be washed by the blood of the lamb and standing on the promises of Christ our King &Saviour. 
Your Support to aid us purchase a good Camera to enable us create more Inspirational content amidst this lock down is highly welcome : jehovahshalomug@gmail.com 

This Medley Contains two Hymns :
1. Are you washed in the blood?  which was written by ELISHA HOFFMAN in 1878 in ohio. 
2.Standing on the Promises of Christ! which was written in 1886, by Russell Kelso Carter
